{"tid":325301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇腦共狗] 被屈CIA佔中指揮 英籍記者：未去過美國","createTime":"2017-07-17T06:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T06:44:41.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c24a4713aa20f1c691b6076ac51c5f745e3c044","tid":325301,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"Richard Scotford與朋友遭親中共人士包圍指罵後，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>愛港行動」召集人陳淨心在facebook指控他們是佔領中環「現場指揮」，更有人在WhatsApp流傳Richard是美國中情局(CIA)人員</strong></span>。本身是英國人的Richard幽默稱，從未去過美國，但可能有點像Jason Bourne(電影《叛諜追擊》男主角，由麥迪文飾演)，或許因此被當作CIA。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他建議對方至少應指控他是MI6(英國軍情六處)</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\nRichard在1996年來港，起初來港在一間酒吧工作，後來教授英文、經營生意。他一直對中國和中國歷史感興趣，並經常就中國政治撰文，2010年在香港中文大學修畢中國研究碩士學位，他專攻意見新聞(opinion journalism)，撰文記錄示威過程和撰寫評論。<br />\n<br />\n9.28雨傘運動爆發，警方向示威者首發的催淚彈正正在Richard上方爆開，他起初以為是煙霧，還叫示威者不用逃跑，當時不能相信警察以催淚彈對付示威者，但警方施放一輪催淚彈後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人開始唱Beyond的歌曲，令他畢生難忘</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n近年他深入採訪反水貨示威等，在facebook和twitter分別有近8000人和1300人追蹤。他亦向網媒投稿，包括HKFP、立場新聞、Real HK News、BC Magazine和熱血時報等。"},{"pid":"85ccef5231c67b7d5a0e6a69de928f8a263a8630","tid":325301,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"建議對方至少應指控他是MI6(英國軍情六處)。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c69cb1564ae5e780a63cb28661a6d00c6014ab1","tid":325301,"uid":14675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議對方至少應指控他是MI6(英國軍情六處)。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾廢中廢佬淨係識美帝CIA<br />\n邊會知有MI6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756e1a05e8de2617fbc303d1fa3ea0fc91aae972","tid":325301,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"應該就黎當街燒白皮豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36a916a5fc9ce80512c02c066d0a49b5c3ed1f4","tid":325301,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議對方至少應指控他是MI6(英國軍情六處)。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾廢中廢佬淨係識美帝CIA<br />\n邊會知有MI6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咁多年鐵金剛都無人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}